      "title": "Geekatplay Transition Showcase",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "1. Load or upload a first clip into the left GAP video loader.\n2. Load or upload a second clip into the right GAP video loader.\n3. Tweak the transition, text overlay, freeze, and speed-ramp settings.\n4. Queue the workflow to render a muxed preview video into ComfyUI/output/Geekatplay/VideoEditorSuite.\n5. No extra checkpoints, VAEs, or text encoders are required for this workflow. Put source videos in ComfyUI/input or upload them directly in GAPLoadVideoUI."
